name: RECREIO
description:
The project aims to show the plurality of Carioca women and tell a little bit of the history of each place.
RECREIO: This is one of the youngest neighborhoods in the city of Rio de Janeiro. It has 2 important ecological spaces in the city and both of them have the main objective of preserving the biodiversity, being possible to observe the presence of animals such as birds, crabs, lizards, and even endangered species.
